{"tid":845203,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"原來日日飲台式野飲真係會大波","createTime":"2018-10-02T12:53:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T13:49:21.000Z","uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c961b077eff0a467fe35a21c8b9f862ad6834b90","tid":845203,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T12:53:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n頭先喺街撞到個中學同學<br />\n熟又唔算熟<br />\n因為佢中學真係平平凡凡咁<br />\n個樣就唔差既，係冇波<br />\n<br />\n但頭先見返佢個下真係嚇左一嚇<br />\n無啦啦對波升左幾個cup<br />\n目測應該由a 變d<br />\n問佢係咪拍拖修練返黎<br />\n點知佢答我日日都一杯珍奶<br />\n<br />\n咁多位平胸絲打有福鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b123ccd504fe9c68c8cd211e710d9a68edd9196e","tid":845203,"uid":63845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T12:54:05.000Z","msg":"pad"},{"pid":"b91584a0b137e4b779f922553d80d93c1335cd9e","tid":845203,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b123ccd504fe9c68c8cd211e710d9a68edd9196e","tid":845203,"uid":63845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T12:54:05.000Z","msg":"pad"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T12:54:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n科勞狗"},{"pid":"72a323eda14d48f51ce2987b6165cb433a966c4d","tid":845203,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T12:54:29.000Z","msg":"moto"},{"pid":"f95efd8297d81f5f740471f91b231fbc6cb78703","tid":845203,"uid":63845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b91584a0b137e4b779f922553d80d93c1335cd9e","tid":845203,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b123ccd504fe9c68c8cd211e710d9a68edd9196e","tid":845203,"uid":63845,